# Cursor Rules

Read `.ai/global-architecture-principles.md` and relevant ADRs before changing code.

## Mandatory Constraints

- TypeScript everywhere with strict mode.
- Feature-oriented clean architecture.
- No business logic in React components.
- Domain layer must not import React, browser APIs, FFmpeg, workers, Zustand, UI, or infrastructure.
- Application layer depends on domain and ports, not concrete adapters.
- Infrastructure implements ports.
- UI calls application use cases only.
- No audio uploads or server-side audio processing.
- FFmpeg.wasm runs in workers.
- Large batch workflows must avoid eager full-file reads.
- Accessibility, privacy, testability, and memory safety are required.

## Required Workflow

1. Identify affected feature and layer.
2. Verify dependency direction.
3. Make the smallest correct change.
4. Add tests.
5. Update docs or ADRs when architecture changes.
